Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:07.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛が愛を重すぎるって理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:11.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}憎しみに変わっていく前に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:13.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}何もかもがそうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:18.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}バツの悪い事情にはいつもフタして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:21.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}食わせもののリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:27.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:32.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}気づかず通りすぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:39.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}壊しあって　分かりあってた事も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:49.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認めないで　立ち向かった時の
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:55.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちていく時のイメージから　逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:22:00.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ああ、何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:07.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}きみの眼　その手のぬくもりを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:10.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}「愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ」って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:14.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}きみは呟いて　信じることが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:17.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}怖くて泣いたんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:19.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}弱さを知って　強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:23.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:28.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}本当の愛を知るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:07.07,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛因愛而愈加沉重 卻拒絕理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:11.55,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在愛變為恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:13.65,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}所有一切皆是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:18.70,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}窘迫的永遠是這眼前的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.52,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}彷彿被吞噬之物的寫實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.83,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在這被扭曲的進退兩難之時代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:27.79,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使海誓山盟的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:32.14,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也漸行著冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:39.57,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}毀滅與理解之物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.42,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}早已被遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.95,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}這難道是滅亡之盡頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:49.34,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}否認這一切 挺身面對之時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:55.74,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即將殞落之時 都不會逃離眼前的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:22:00.41,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}啊，無論如何也要找尋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:07.09,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}你的雙眸 雙手的溫存
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:10.60,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}說什麼「愛總是只給我帶來傷害」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:14.27,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君之低聲細語 深信之言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:17.27,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}是在恐懼中哭泣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:19.42,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認識著軟弱 渴望著堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:23.23,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}當不再恐懼而滿懷信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:28.03,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}那將是真實的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RESOLUS遭到MS襲擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的傢伙 連勸告都沒有就進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方的MS裡好像混有新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯 那些傢伙是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PROUD的營救作戰還是延期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 如此更應該把計劃提前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這關乎到眾多同志的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能失去他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去聯絡營救部隊 通知他們變更作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聯邦政府為了剿滅反政府勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將投入政府直屬的治安維持部隊 並展開活動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治安維持部隊將與聯邦保安局合作 謀求更高的功效…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才司令部發出了獨立治安維持部隊的調動命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看傳說中的A-LAWS也好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個部隊有很多的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能得到內情的報告 會很有幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我就是這個意思 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬內金大校打來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 那件事情考慮得怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 不用急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢考慮就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:14.24,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}L4(拉格朗日L4點) 殖民衛星PROUD
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 保持狀態 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的真不錯啊 新來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經來了半年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該用沙慈·庫洛斯洛特來稱呼我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是埃迪·宮阪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們懷疑你是KATARON派來的間諜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮阪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼突然 想幹什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟我們走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要抓我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:03:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的新型航空巡洋艦開始駛向L4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和王留美的情報一致
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搭乘Seravee出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還活著的話 一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:25.60,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}殖民衛星PROUD 高重力工業區劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}同區劃內 礦石精煉區域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種…高重力下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連機械也不使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要停下 R81
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍惜生命的話 就別說話快幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去幹活 R81
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離PROUD還有2300
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子的散佈維持通常濃度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑江中校 好像是發現KATARON的船了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 偵察部隊發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是朝PROUD去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型自走機器人的狀況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.19,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(568,672)}Automaton
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全機均在可啟動狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府勢力討伐作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahead第1小隊 準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahead第1小隊 準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahead和搭載自走機器人的莢艙的連接完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機能無異常 一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基寧大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號機的哈勒維准尉是初戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她感受一下戰場的氣氛即可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基寧小隊 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也不放過...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這點事 怎能叫我屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在宇宙的話 總有一天能見到露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你不像當過兵的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是KATARON的人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被牽連進來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你小子運氣不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡運氣不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快躲起來 作戰馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰是指什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是接到躲避的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算把我丟在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RIARDO部隊 前期行動 結束!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營救作戰 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始侵入第7區域的重力系統!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵入完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力竟然…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的同志!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 正上方確認到MS存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新型機在!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…A-LAWS麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉格中尉 攻擊敵方部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勒維准尉在當前坐標待機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按照原定計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行新型自走機器人的性能實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莢艙 分離
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型自走機器人啟動開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍用自走機器人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃… 對人兵器…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS幹的好事嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·庫洛斯洛特…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的狗雜種們!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號機麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號機 判斷得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…還是沒變……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…從那個時候起 一點都沒……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E傳感器有反應?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的增援嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才沒有在追求 這樣子的……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…洛克昂也好 我也好……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才沒追求這種樣子的世界!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上面罩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉 那機影是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那種GN粒子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自走機器人的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在減少?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉 上面來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun… Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 為何你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼現在要出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是要破環
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你們的行為 忍無可忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要驅逐你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam不過是5年前的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能和Ahead對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三號機 掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 哈勒維准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂 我們自己來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眾多戰友死於你們之手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日讓我來報
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的時代 結束了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力場!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背部居然有臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勒維准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回話 三號機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在打探A-LAWS的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞·愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德發現了Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在PROUD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王小姐的情報好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會驚訝的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到拉塞先生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著啊 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就能使用Exia的太陽爐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PROUD那裡出現了Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得謝謝他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠此得以救出倖存的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將可能成為被武力介入的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們和我們志趣相投 席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣質變化不小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你卻沒什麼變化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還像從前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常被人這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天行者的麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在駕駛Gundam嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·庫洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5年前開始的武力介入也有你份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道麼? 你們的所作所為害死多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是拜你們所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因為你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心上人受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家屬和親人被殺害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一的親姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因受到天行者的牽連…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殺害了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易斯也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會遇到Gundam的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來我們的存在價值就更高了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種傢伙能進A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:19:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲·哈勒維
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來你也有了戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡本斯 有客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立治安維持部隊和新Gundam發生接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個Gundam是否屬於天行者還尚未得知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒對自己是處女座感到那麼自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍獨立治安維持部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前來迎接索瑪·皮瑞斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是第五機動部隊所屬安德雷·斯米爾諾夫少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候加入A-LAWS的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有義務回答你 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 塞魯哥·斯米盧諾夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有射殺剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人的話就和你們一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要感謝剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是他帶你來此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就被當作反聯邦的KATARON成員處死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:22:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太不瞭解現實了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如自己親眼去見識一下世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你找我麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON成員 萊爾·狄蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安局的麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來迎接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名叫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者的Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你也將成為Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾·狄蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不! 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.94,0:24:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望毀滅之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背道而馳之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為各種思想紛擾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今 00 Gundam覺醒而至
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 Twin Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.57,0:24:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 驅逐Gundam的Gundam


